This paper deals with information retrieval and natural language processing techniques to classify and recommend web pages from web archives. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also involves techniques related to web crawling and web archiving, which falls under cs.DL (Digital Libraries). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques for classification, which is related to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with cybersecurity and privacy concerns related to web archiving, which falls under cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper discusses the quality of web archives, which is related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
